verbose_text: However, an ANOVA for grass photosynthetic pathway type (C3, C4 and mixed) showed that there was a significant difference (p = 0.003) with C4 grasslands increasing SOC by 0.056 (5.6%; StDev = 0.341), and C3 grasses and mixed grass decreasing SOC by -0.155 (-15.5%; StDev = 0.233) and -0.25 (-25%; StDev = 0.435), respectively (XREF_TABLE).
evidence: C4 grasslands increasing SOC by 0.056 (5.6%; StDev = 0.341), and C3 grasses and mixed grass decreasing SOC
